266	#### `WeekContent` (static catalog, keyed by week 1-40)
267	| Field | Type |
268	|---|---|
269	| `fruitEmoji` | `String` |
270	| `fruitSize` | `String` |
271	| `bodyChanges` | `List<String>` |
272	| `babyDevelopment` | `String` |
273	| `selfCareTips` | `List<SelfCareTip>` |
274	
275	#### `SelfCareTip`
276	| Field | Type |
277	|---|---|
278	| `title` | `String` |
279	| `detail` | `String` |
280	
281	---
282	
283	## 9. Motion
284	
285	### Page Transitions
286	- **Type:** Horizontal slide with PageView default physics
287	- **Duration:** 300ms (PageView built-in)
288	- **Curve:** `Curves.easeInOut`
289	
290	### Card Entrance
291	- **Type:** Fade + slight upward slide
292	- **Duration:** 300ms
293	- **Delay:** 50ms stagger between cards
294	- **Curve:** `Curves.easeOut`
295	
296	### Self-Care Tip Expansion
297	- **Type:** Height animation with fade
298	- **Duration:** 200ms
299	- **Curve:** `Curves.easeOut`
300	
301	### Bottom Card
302	- **Type:** No entrance animation (always visible)
303	- **Shadow:** Subtle pulse on week change — 200ms shadow intensity increase/decrease
304	
305	---
306	
307	## 10. Accessibility
308	
309	### Semantic Labels
310	- **Week Hero:** `"Pregnancy week {n}, {fruitSize} size, {countdown} until due date"`
311	- **Body Changes:** `"Body changes this week: {count} items"`
312	- **Baby Development:** `"Baby development for week {n}: {description excerpt}"`
313	- **Self-Care Tip:** `"Self-care tip {n}: {title}. Tap to expand"`
314	- **Due Date Summary:** `"Due date: {date}, {days} days remaining, {trimester}"`
315	- **PageView swipe:** `"Week {n} of 40. Use swipe gestures to navigate weeks"`
316	
317	### Focus Order
318	1. Back button (AppBar leading)
319	2. Week Hero (implicitly focusable as first content)
320	3. Body Changes card
321	4. Baby Development card
322	5. Self-Care Tips (each tip focusable in order)
323	6. Due Date Summary card
324	
325	### Contrast Notes
326	- All text meets WCAG AA contrast (4.5:1 minimum for body, 3:1 for large text)
327	- Deep Graphite (#1F2937) on Morning Mist (#FAFAFA) = 12.6:1 ✓
328	- Stone Grey (#6B7280) on Morning Mist = 4.7:1 ✓
329	- White on Lavender Bloom = 4.2:1 ✓
330	
331	---
332	
333	## 11. Anti-Patterns
334	
335	### Banned
336	- **No default platform colors** — all colors from design token palette
337	- **No arbitrary text sizing** — use type scale (57pt hero, 28pt title, 22pt section header, 16pt body)
338	- **No inconsistent spacing** — use 8pt base unit
339	- **No bottom nav** — this screen hides bottom navigation per spec
340	- **No FAB** — this screen has no FAB per spec
341	- **No hardcoded week content** — all week content from `WeekContent` catalog
342	- **No SliverAppBar inside PageView** — incompatible scroll physics; use standard AppBar
343	- **No touch targets under 48dp**
344	- **No pure black (#000000)** — use Deep Graphite (#1F2937)
345	- **No pure white (#FFFFFF) for body text** — use Deep Graphite on light surfaces
346	
347	### Constraints
348	- PageView cannot be nested inside another scrollable that conflicts (no SliverAppBar in same scaffold)
349	- Due Date Summary must not overlap content when keyboard is visible
350	- Week navigation must not reset expanded tip state (accordion local to each week's tip set)
