| Tertiary / success | Night Mint | #34D399 |\n60\t| Surface background | Deep Twilight | #1E1B2E |\n61\t| Scaffold background | Night Sky | #13111C |\n62\t| Primary text | Soft Pearl | #F3F4F6 |\n63\t| Secondary text | Muted Silver | #9CA3AF |\n64\t| Border / divider | Deep Border | #2D2B3A |\n65\t| Error | Muted Coral | #F87171 |\n66\t| Surface overlay | Charcoal Surface | #252336 |\n67\t\n68\t---\n69\t\n70\t## Spacing Scale\n71\t\n72\t| Token | Points |\n73\t|---|---|\n74\t| Base unit | 8 |\n75\t| xxs | 4 |\n76\t| xs | 8 |\n77\t| sm | 12 |\n78\t| md | 16 |\n79\t| lg | 24 |\n80\t| xl | 32 |\n81\t| xxl | 48 |\n82\t\n83\t---\n84\t\n85\t## Corner Radius Scale\n86\t\n87\t| Token | Points |\n88\t|---|---|\n89\t| sm | 8 |\n90\t| md | 12 |\n91\t| lg | 16 |\n92\t| full | 999 (pill) |\n93\t\n94\t---\n95\t\n96\t## Type Scale\n97\t\n98\t| Role | Size | Weight | Line Height |\n99\t|---|---|---|---|\n100\t| Hero display | 57pt | Bold (700) | 64pt |\n101\t| Screen title | 28pt | SemiBold (600) | 36pt |\n102\t| Section header | 22pt | SemiBold (600) | 28pt |\n103\t| Subtitle | 16pt | Medium (500) | 24pt |\n104\t| Body | 16pt | Regular (400) | 24pt |\n105\t| Body small | 14pt | Regular (400) | 20pt |\n106\t| Button label | 14pt | SemiBold (600) | 20pt |\n107\t| Caption | 11pt | Medium (500) | 16pt |\n108\t\n109\t---\n110\t\n111\t## Motion Tokens\n112\t\n113\t| Token | Duration | Easing Character |\n114\t|---|---|---|\n115\t| Micro-interactions | 200ms | Snappy ease-out |\n116\t| Page transitions | 300ms | Smooth deceleration |\n117\t| Hero transitions | 350ms | Fast-out-slow-in |\n118\t| Bottom sheets | 250ms | Smooth deceleration |\n119\t| Staggered reveals | 50ms delay per item | — |\n120\t| Pull-to-refresh | 150ms | Quick snap |\n121\t| Tab indicator | 200ms | Ease-in-out |\n122\t\n123\t---\n124\t\n125\t## Anti-Patterns (Banned)\n126\t\n127\t- No platform default colors — use design system palette only\n128\t- No ad-hoc text sizing — use type scale only\n129\t- No inconsistent